♪That lets me keep smiling so brightly♪

120
00:08:41,540 --> 00:08:48,860
♪The faint light
slipping through my fingers♪

121
00:08:51,740 --> 00:08:54,940
♪Writes down my persistence♪

122
00:08:56,020 --> 00:08:59,180
♪What would I be without you?♪

123
